originalText.text: I used to have a fear of going to the dentist, but Dr. Chang helped me overcome my fears. He's a great dentist and knows how to comfort his patients. My wife introduced me to him yrs ago and now I've been his patient for 3 yrs and highly recommend him to anyone. I recommended him to my mother and now my mother is one of his patients. Dr. Chang is terrific, you won't be disappointed.

originalText.text: Dr. Chang is the best dentist I have ever had.  He's my wife's dentist.  I started going to him after we started dating.  He's very skilled.  I have complete trust on his work.  There's never any discomfort on any work I had done, including cavities and a couple of crowns.  Highly recommended.
